    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Since most classes in Zend Framework don't expose many public properties, I propose that a getView() method is added to gain access to the view on Zend_Controller_Action_Helper_ViewRenderer.</p>

<p>I've noticed many people asking how to access the view within the ViewRenderer helper and obviously, many of them don't look at the properties because most properties in the API are protected.</p>

